trans-unit.source: The exception that is thrown when multiple filters match, but only one was expected.
trans-unit.target: 當多個篩選條件相符，但預期只有一個相符時所擲回的例外狀況。

trans-unit.source: The list of filters includes the filters that caused the exception to be thrown.
trans-unit.target: 篩選條件清單會包含導致擲回例外狀況的篩選條件。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.MultipleFilterMatchesException" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.MultipleFilterMatchesException" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.MultipleFilterMatchesException" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.MultipleFilterMatchesException" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo" /> that contains all the data required to serialize the exception.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo" />，其中包含序列化例外狀況時所需要的所有資料。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext" /> that specifies the source and destination of the stream.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext" />，指定資料流的來源和目的地。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.MultipleFilterMatchesException" /> class with serialization information and streaming context specified.
trans-unit.target: 使用指定的序列化 (Serialization) 資訊與資料流 (Streaming) 內容，初始化 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.MultipleFilterMatchesException" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.MultipleFilterMatchesException" /> class with a specified error message.
trans-unit.target: 使用指定的錯誤訊息，初始化 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.MultipleFilterMatchesException" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.MultipleFilterMatchesException" /> class with a specified error message and a collection of filters.
trans-unit.target: 使用指定的錯誤訊息和篩選條件的集合，初始化 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.MultipleFilterMatchesException" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.MultipleFilterMatchesException" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.MultipleFilterMatchesException" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.MultipleFilterMatchesException" /> class with a specified error message, an exception, and a collection of filters.
trans-unit.target: 使用指定的錯誤訊息、例外狀況和篩選條件集合，初始化 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.MultipleFilterMatchesException" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of filters that caused the exception to be thrown.
trans-unit.target: 取得導致擲回例外狀況的篩選條件集合。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Collections.ObjectModel.Collection`1" /> of type <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.MessageFilter" /> that contains the filters that caused the exception to be thrown.
trans-unit.target: 類型為 <see cref="T:System.Collections.ObjectModel.Collection`1" /> 的 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.MessageFilter" />，其中包含導致擲回例外狀況的篩選條件。
